      <h2>The Story of Running Creek Sourdough</h2>
      <p>It all started with a simple starter and a deep respect for the slow, natural process of fermentation. At Running Creek Sourdough, we believe that true artisan bread takes time, patience, and the highest quality ingredients.</p>
      <p>Each loaf we bake is a labor of love, crafted by hand in our home microbakery. We use traditional techniques and long fermentation periods to develop the complex flavors and airy textures that define real sourdough.</p>
      <p>Whether it's our signature Country White or our rotating specialty loaves, every bread that leaves our oven tells a story of tradition, craft, and the simple joy of a perfect crust.</p>
